    <!-- About Start -->
    <div class="container-xxl py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row g-4 align-items-end mb-4">
                <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
                    <img class="img-fluid rounded" src="~/finanza-1.0.0/img/about.jpg">
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
                    <p class="d-inline-block border rounded text-primary fw-semi-bold py-1 px-3">About Us</p>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        Premium Deadline Management is a cloud portal that works as a Companies House filing
                        deadline manager, allowing accountants to manage their clients' Companies House filing
                        deadlines.
                    </p>
                    <div class="border rounded p-4">
                        <nav>
                            <div class="nav nav-tabs mb-3" id="nav-tab" role="tablist">
                                <button class="nav-link fw-semi-bold active" id="nav-story-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab"
                                        data-bs-target="#nav-story" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="nav-story"
                                        aria-selected="true">
                                    Story
                                </button>
                                <button class="nav-link fw-semi-bold" id="nav-mission-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab"
                                        data-bs-target="#nav-mission" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="nav-mission"
                                        aria-selected="false">
                                    Mission
                                </button>
                                <button class="nav-link fw-semi-bold" id="nav-vision-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab"
                                        data-bs-target="#nav-vision" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="nav-vision"
                                        aria-selected="false">
                                    Vision
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </nav>
                        <div class="tab-content" id="nav-tabContent">
                            <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="nav-story" role="tabpanel"
                                 aria-labelledby="nav-story-tab">
                                <p>
                                    We saw accountants struggling with tracking deadlines for hundreds of clients,
                                    leading to missed filings and penalties.
                                </p>
                                <p class="mb-0">
                                    Premium Deadline Management was created
                                    to solve this problem—providing a seamless, reliable, and automated solution
                                    to keep accountants in control.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="tab-pane fade" id="nav-mission" role="tabpanel"
                                 aria-labelledby="nav-mission-tab">
                                <p>
                                    We simplify Companies House deadline tracking, ensuring accountants stay
                                    compliant without stress.
                                </p>
                                <p class="mb-0">
                                    Our goal is to eliminate missed filings and penalties
                                    through an efficient, user-friendly system.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="tab-pane fade" id="nav-vision" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="nav-vision-tab">
                                <p>
                                    To be the most trusted and innovative solution for deadline management,
                                    helping accountancy practices stay organized, efficient, and penalty-free.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="border rounded p-4 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
