                                <div class="col-md-6" style="min-height: 350px;">
                                    <div class="position-relative h-100">
                                        <img class="rounded w-100 h-100" src="~/finanza-1.0.0/img/service-1.jpg"
                                             style="object-fit: cover;" alt="">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <h3 class="mb-4">Client Deadline Prioritisation</h3>
                                    <p class="mb-4">
                                        Focus your team on the most critical filings first with a clear,
                                        risk-based prioritisation model. Keep workstreams structured and
                                        improve on-time submission performance.
                                    </p>
                                    <p><i class="fa fa-check text-primary me-3"></i>Priority-based deadline scoring</p>
                                    <p><i class="fa fa-check text-primary me-3"></i>Critical filing visibility</p>
                                    <p><i class="fa fa-check text-primary me-3"></i>Escalation for high-risk items</p>
                                    <a href="" class="btn btn-primary py-3 px-5 mt-3">Read More</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="tab-pane-3">
                            <div class="row g-4">
                                <div class="col-md-6" style="min-height: 350px;">
                                    <div class="position-relative h-100">
                                        <img class="rounded w-100 h-100" src="~/finanza-1.0.0/img/service-3.jpg"
                                             style="object-fit: cover;" alt="">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <h3 class="mb-4">Easier Workflow</h3>
                                    <p class="mb-4">
                                        Premium Deadline Management is here to help! We have created a Companies House deadline tracker to overcome the hassle accountancy practices normally need to bear!
                                    </p>
                                    <p><i class="fa fa-check text-primary me-3"></i>Centralized Dashboard for All Clients</p>
                                    <p><i class="fa fa-check text-primary me-3"></i>Real-Time Deadline Updates</p>
                                    <p><i class="fa fa-check text-primary me-3"></i>Secure Cloud Storage</p>
                                    <a href="" class="btn btn-primary py-3 px-5 mt-3">Read More</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="tab-pane-4">
                            <div class="row g-4">
                                <div class="col-md-6" style="min-height: 350px;">
                                    <div class="position-relative h-100">
                                        <img class="rounded w-100 h-100" src="~/finanza-1.0.0/img/service-4.jpg"
                                             style="object-fit: cover;" alt="">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <h3 class="mb-4">Auto Deadline Tracking</h3>
                                    <p class="mb-4">
                                        Automatically updates due dates for Accounts submission and CS01 - Confirmation Statement. This seamless integration ensures you always stay on top of your deadlines.
                                    </p>
                                    <p><i class="fa fa-check text-primary me-3"></i>Automated Accounts Submission Tracking</p>
                                    <p><i class="fa fa-check text-primary me-3"></i>Confirmation Statement Alert</p>
                                    <p><i class="fa fa-check text-primary me-3"></i>Custom Deadline Configurations</p>
                                    <a href="" class="btn btn-primary py-3 px-5 mt-3">Read More</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
